rasshoppers, moths and cockroaches, as well as small mammals and birds. Its breeding behaviour is almost unknown but it is thought to nest in the old nesting cavities created by woodpeckers or barbets. Conservation status The IUCN (International Union for Conservation of Nature) Red List, classifies the red-chested owlet as least concern, since the population is believed to be stable and has a sizable range. References The Owl Pages", "shortSummary": "The red-chested owlet (Glaucidium tephronotum) is a species of owl in the family Strigidae, native to the African tropical rainforest. Its…", "locations": ["理查德·鮑德勒·夏普", "熱帶森林", "刚果共和国", "刚果民主共和国", "乌干达"], "lat": -1.44, "lng": 15.556, "imageUrl": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/63/Glaucidium_tephronotum_in_Uganda_550590424.jpg/960px-Glaucidium_tephronotum_in_Uganda_550590424.jpg", "kingdomId": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylumId": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "classId": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genusId": "taxonomy-genus-glaucidium", "speciesId": "taxonomy-species-glaucidium-tephronotum", "taxonomyIds": {"kingdom": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylum": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "class": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genus": "taxonomy-genus-glaucidium", "species": "taxonomy-species-glaucidium-tephronotum"}, "expandable": true, "x": 206.75, "y": -437.55, "z": 756.03}, {"id": "taxonomy-species-glaucidium-tephronotum", "name": "Red-chested owlet", "latinName": "Glaucidium tephronotum", "type": "taxonomy", "taxonomyLevel": "species", "summary": "Red-chested owlet（Glaucidium tephronotum）是图谱中的分类级分类节点，当前关联1种鸟类，如Red-chested owlet。", "expandable": true, "memberCount": 1, "x": 206.75, "y": -437.55, "z": 743.36}, {"id": "taxonomy-genus-glaucidium", "name": "Glaucidium", "latinName": "Glaucidium", "type": "taxonomy", "taxonomyLevel": "genus", "summary": "Glaucidium（Glaucidium）是图谱中的分类级分类节点，当前关联25种鸟类，如花头鸺鹠、Pearl-spotted owlet、Northern pygmy owl等25种鸟类。", "expandable": true, "memberCount": 25, "x": 541.04, "y": 192